==English==

===Homophones===
*[[troll]]

===Noun===
'''trawl'''
# A [[net]] used for [[trawling]].
# A long [[fishing line]] having many short lines bearing [[hook]]s attached to it; a [[setline]].

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|trawl||}}
# To take fish, or other marine animals, with a trawl.
# To [[fish]] from a slow moving [[boat]].
# To make an [[exhaustive]] [[search]] for something within a [[defined]] [[area]].

====Translations====
French: [[chaluter]] (1,2)

